title: con_exo_1
characteristics_ch1: disease state: healthy
treatment_protocol_ch1: Serum was extracted and exosomes were extracted by kit(exoquick).
growth_protocol_ch1: Peripheral blood of healthy individuals and newly diagnosed myeloma patients were collected with non-anticoagulant tubes, placed at 4 ℃ for no more than 1 hour
extract_protocol_ch1: Kit extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.(miRNeasy Micro Kit)
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 130 ng total RNA (Affymetrix microRNA 4.0).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 48C on GeneChip . GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Hewlett-Packard GeneArray Scanner G3000 7G.
description: Gene expression data from healthy individuals serum  exosomes
data_processing: The data were analyzed with RMA using Affymetrix default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method. The trimmed mean target intensity of each array was arbitrarily set to 100.
